To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Minnesota Government Data Practices Act, I hereby request the following records:

The incident report and any supplements, such as police narratives, produced in relation to the shooting/shots fired/suicide incident at Hand in Hand Montessori School on January 26, 2015.

In the event that there are fees, I would request a waiver, as I am a member of a nonprofit media outlet and these records will be used in the public interest. The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes. 

I would prefer the request filed electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 business days.

Sincerely,

Ben Baker

To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the The Missouri Sunshine Law, I hereby request the following records:

Your agency's listings, catalogs, registers or logs of Sunshine Law Requests for calendar years of 2019, 2020, 2021, 2022 and 2023. These listings, catalogs, registers or logs should include a request date, description of records requested, requester organization (if applicable) and current status of the requests.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 3 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Kevin Hawkins

title: MO Civil Rights Cases/Conspiracy Against Rights/Deprivation of Rights Under Color of Law - 2019, 2020, 2021, 2022 and 2023

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the The Missouri Sunshine Law, I hereby request the following records:

Court document or court records related to complaint filings or lawsuit filings, prosecutions or convictions related to cases for Conspiracy Against Rights and/or Deprivation of Rights Under Color of Law in the years of 2019, 2020, 2021, 2022 and 2023 filed in Missouri Eastern District Courts, Missouri Western District Courts or Missouri Southern District Courts relating to civil rights violations by employee(s) of Missouri law enforcement agencies or any other local, state or federal law enforcement agencies.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 3 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Kevin Hawkins
